            223.12799072265625,
            359.31597900390625,
            240.31198120117188
          ],
          "text": "A. Licensing of Urban Co-operative Banks (UCBs)",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            246.23997497558594,
            523.3599243164062,
            262.6199645996094
          ],
          "text": "1. \nNo fresh proposals for organization of new UCBs or for conversion of co-",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37996673583984,
            266.9399719238281,
            526.6610107421875,
            283.3199768066406
          ],
          "text": "operative credit societies into UCBs are being considered by Reserve Bank of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37996673583984,
            287.6399841308594,
            136.4159698486328,
            304.0199890136719
          ],
          "text": "India.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37997436523438,
            314.843994140625,
            523.7171630859375,
            330.7200012207031
          ],
          "text": "In this context, Urban Co-operative Banks shall mean Primary Co-operative",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-ItalicMT",
            "flags": 2,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": true
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37997436523438,
            335.54400634765625,
            523.7199096679688,
            351.4200134277344
          ],
          "text": "Banks as defined under section 5(ccv) read with Section 56 of Banking",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-ItalicMT",
            "flags": 2,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": true
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37997436523438,
            356.2440185546875,
            217.16146850585938,
            372.1200256347656
          ],
          "text": "Regulation Act, 1949.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-ItalicMT",
            "flags": 2,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": true
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            382.24798583984375,
            367.9598083496094,
            399.4319763183594
          ],
          "text": "B. Categorization of UCBs for Regulatory Purposes",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b13",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            409.1399841308594,
            526.6573486328125,
            425.5199890136719
          ],
          "text": "2. \nGiven the heterogeneity in the urban cooperative sector, a four-tiered regulatory",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b14",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37997436523438,
            429.8399963378906,
            526.6610717773438,
            446.2200012207031
          ],
          "text": "framework has been adopted to balance the spirit of mutuality and cooperation",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b15",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37997436523438,
            450.5400085449219,
            526.659912109375,
            466.9200134277344
          ],
          "text": "more prevalent in banks of smaller sizes and those with limited area of operation",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b16",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37997436523438,
            471.2400207519531,
            526.6585083007812,
            487.6200256347656
          ],
          "text": "vis-à-vis the growth ambitions of the large-sized UCBs to spread their area of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b17",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37997436523438,
            491.9400329589844,
            526.6558837890625,
            508.3200378417969
          ],
          "text": "operation and undertake more complex business activities. Accordingly, the",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b18",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37997436523438,
            512.6400756835938,
            493.8359680175781,
            529.0200805664062
          ],
          "text": "UCBs are categorized into the following four tiers for regulatory purposes:",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b19",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37997436523438,
            539.340087890625,
            522.8824462890625,
            555.7200927734375
          ],
          "text": "(1) Tier 1 - All unit UCBs and salary earners' UCBs (irrespective of deposit size),",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b20",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            121.6199722290039,
            559.9801025390625,
            406.41595458984375,
            576.360107421875
          ],
          "text": "and all other UCBs having deposits up to ₹100 crore;",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b21",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37994384765625,
            586.6801147460938,
            522.8759155273438,
            603.0601196289062
          ],
          "text": "(2) Tier 2 - UCBs with deposits of more than ₹100 crore and up to ₹1000 crore;",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b22",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37991333007812,
            613.380126953125,
            522.8798217773438,
            629.7601318359375
          ],
          "text": "(3) Tier 3 - UCBs with deposits of more than ₹1000 crore and up to ₹10,000",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b23",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            121.61992645263672,
            634.080078125,
            155.6159210205078,
            650.4600830078125
          ],
          "text": "crore;",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b24",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37992858886719,
            660.7800903320312,
            421.3559265136719,
            677.1600952148438
          ],
          "text": "(4) Tier 4 - UCBs with deposits of more than ₹10,000 crore.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b25",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99993896484375,
            687.4801025390625,
            526.65869140625,
            703.860107421875
          ],
          "text": "3. \nThe deposits referred to above shall be reckoned as per the audited balance",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b26",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            100.37993621826172,
            708.1799926757812,
            456.0959777832031,
            724.56005859375
          ],
          "text": "sheet as of 31st March of the immediately preceding financial year.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
